    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>节奏对战</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与《Hailing From the Abyss》一同踏上欢乐的节奏之旅！探索各种各样的关卡，每个关卡都由精心设计的独特敌人镇守，搭配着原创音乐，以匹配游戏迷人的像素图形风格。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1797480/extras/4382ba6056809c39235408d8fb4720a6.poster.avif?t=1763474043\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1797480/extras/4382ba6056809c39235408d8fb4720a6.webm?t=1763474043\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1797480/extras/4382ba6056809c39235408d8fb4720a6.mp4?t=1763474043\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>在归乡的火车上，主角戴着耳机睡着后，开始在《Hailing from the Abyss》的世界中进行冒险，在熟悉的场景中，在一首首独特的旋律中，面对自己的过去。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏特色</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-超过20个配有独特音乐的原创关卡。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-超过6个章节的丰富有趣的剧情，15种独特敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-能力提升和对战系统。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-玩家可以在对战中使用道具。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-2D像素艺术风格以及充满活力的游戏氛围</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1797480/extras/549b044249b2bda61b7ddd4d6288ffe1.poster.avif?t=1763474043\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1797480/extras/549b044249b2bda61b7ddd4d6288ffe1.webm?t=1763474043\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1797480/extras/549b044249b2bda61b7ddd4d6288ffe1.mp4?t=1763474043\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏制作人员</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >开发者 / 游戏导演： @JiwooLee</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >谱面设计： @Arcwinolivirus</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >艺术： @Admurin, @Christiansim &amp; @Shannon Woods</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >音乐： @LeohPaz, @Russell Raija Harper, @GmdRocket</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >配音： @Madison Lee</p>",
